        <mxCell id="user_logic" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EAF4E8;strokeColor=#82B366;fontColor=#1A3D15;arcSize=8;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" value="&lt;b&gt;Registration Flow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Validate email format&lt;br/&gt;2. Check email uniqueness&lt;br/&gt;3. Hash password (BCrypt)&lt;br/&gt;4. If avatar → call Media Service&lt;br/&gt;5. Save user&lt;br/&gt;6. Return JWT&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;JWT Payload&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;{ sub: userId, role: SELLER, exp: ... }" vertex="1">
