        <mxCell id="media_logic" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF4E6;strokeColor=#D6853A;fontColor=#5C2800;arcSize=8;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" value="&lt;b&gt;Upload Flow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;1. Receive file + optional productId&lt;br/&gt;2. Check size ≤ 2MB → else FILE_TOO_LARGE&lt;br/&gt;3. Check MIME = image/jpeg | image/png&lt;br/&gt;   (check real MIME, not just extension!)&lt;br/&gt;4. Generate unique filename (UUID)&lt;br/&gt;5. Store file (local /uploads/ or S3)&lt;br/&gt;6. Save metadata to Media DB&lt;br/&gt;7. Return { mediaId, url }&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Storage Layout&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;/uploads/users/{userId}/&lt;br/&gt;/uploads/products/{productId}/&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Security&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Only ownerId match can DELETE" vertex="1">
